  (3.) 2 Chr. 29:13. A Levite of the sons of Asaph.

  (4.) 2 Chr. 26:11. A scribe.

  (5.) 1 Chr. 5:7. A Reubenite chief.

  (6.) One of the chief Levites, who made an offering for the
