12:5).

  (4.) A Levitical musician under Heman his father (1 Chr.
25:4).

  (5.) 1 Chr. 27:19, ruler of Naphtali.

  (6.) One of David's sons (2 Chr. 11:18).

  (7.) A Levite, one of the overseers of the temple offerings (2
